{"id": 2134, "genre": 1001, "title": "你的最佳损友是啥样儿的？", "description": "他们的什么举动会让你产生“这才是真朋友”的感觉？（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 2422, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180122183229jUyzCdopcXnQFDIi.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-01-30T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 262658, "content": "一个眼神，不用说话", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1039344}, {"id": 262659, "content": "“喂”\n“嗯，怎么了，又想哥了？”", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1124201}, {"id": 263684, "content": "在我企图做伤害自己的蠢事的时候，会不远百里地飞来扇我两巴掌)•́⊚•̀(", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1254990}, {"id": 267015, "content": "谈钱不伤感情", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1122868}, {"id": 264200, "content": "没有\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1257750}, {"id": 262665, "content": "说话不需要走脑子，随心即可。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1250250}, {"id": 263945, "content": "安静呆在一起也很舒服", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1255671}, {"id": 262667, "content": "好久不见但是如同昨天刚分别", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1227642}, {"id": 262670, "content": "可以互损，没有什么太大的压力和顾忌", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1250273}, {"id": 262678, "content": "shenzi ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1227106}, {"id": 262679, "content": "互怼，不说话也不尴尬\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1175662}, {"id": 262680, "content": "车也是能借的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1249559}, {"id": 262681, "content": "伤心的时候能陪你聊天聊到天荒地老的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1186744}, {"id": 262682, "content": "毫不留情地击碎幻想", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1067874}, {"id": 262684, "content": "骂醒你，然后拉你一把", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1250386}, {"id": 262685, "content": "很久没见\n再见也不尴尬   永远有话说 且说不完\n哪怕观点不一样  也是觉得这是对方的闪光点\n永远给我正能量", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1236148}, {"id": 262686, "content": "无条件呼之即来挥之即去，自己走了家就让他继续着照顾。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1246007}, {"id": 262687, "content": "交流靠套路", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 188003}, {"id": 263456, "content": "难过的时候，她会对你说\"没关系, 我在这儿喃。\"心里暖暖的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1155797}, {"id": 265248, "content": "我想什么她都知道", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1262513}, {"id": 262689, "content": "互相当爸爸", "image": "img/option/option/20180131101513XebkHQufE3gh7dwO.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 443174}, {"id": 263457, "content": "当面损 背面夸", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1253651}, {"id": 262690, "content": "外向的孤单患者，无！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1036408}, {"id": 262691, "content": "在我需要她们的时候，我随时可以找到，永远也不会嫌弃我！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1250419}, {"id": 262693, "content": "半夜生病毫不顾忌给我打电话，要求我去接她送医院。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1250431}, {"id": 264232, "content": "谈钱的很多啊…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1004233}, {"id": 265260, "content": "不管我怎么跑题最后还是要钱…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1262540}, {"id": 262701, "content": "突然发现，没有这样的人…", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1250341}, {"id": 263470, "content": "会告诉你：你胖了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1182566}, {"id": 263726, "content": "Tttttt", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1246996}, {"id": 262447, "content": "大儿，有没有思念为父", "image": null, "praise_count": 127, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1181346}, {"id": 263727, "content": "Yyyyyyuuu", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1246996}, {"id": 262704, "content": "“开车”开到一半，完美接梗的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1092499}, {"id": 263728, "content": "Yyyyyy", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1246996}, {"id": 262449, "content": "骂你 爱你", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1206568}, {"id": 262450, "content": "借钱的时候还没解释钱就打过来了，真的很感谢", "image": null, "praise_count": 137, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1247813}, {"id": 262452, "content": "不知道味道怎么样", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1220933}, {"id": 263476, "content": "无论怎么损对方他也不会当一回事但是也会损回来", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1251698}, {"id": 262453, "content": "谈钱从来不用绕弯。", "image": null, "praise_count": 418, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1152567}, {"id": 262454, "content": "你是我见过世界上最丑的女人，他说的", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1144137}, {"id": 264758, "content": "感觉自己说什么，损友都会有不一样的观点，结局是：“换个话题！！！”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1260333}, {"id": 268086, "content": "我对她付出的 ，希望她也能照顾点我", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1274966}, {"id": 262455, "content": "一边说着你瘦的不明显，一边还疯狂投喂^_^", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1249635}, {"id": 262456, "content": "就事论事", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 775101}, {"id": 262457, "content": "有什么不开心的事情别放在心里，说出来，让姐也乐乐", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 430264}, {"id": 262458, "content": "互怼", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 753625}, {"id": 266298, "content": "没找到过", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1268321}, {"id": 262973, "content": "不存在的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1058561}, {"id": 262464, "content": "相互有一种自由的感觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 80, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 814778}, {"id": 262721, "content": "互损各种黄腔无底线", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 697517}]}